We will construct an equivalence M\mapsto  T(M) from the category of 1-motives over \mathbb {C} to the category of torsion free mixed Hodge structures H of type
           \big \{ (0,0), (0,-1), (-1,0), (-1,-1) \big \}     

    such that \operatorname {Gr}_{-1}^W(H) is polarisable.
    Furthermore, we will construct isomorphisms
